detail.name: The Greatest Showdown of All Time!
detail.effect: [Activate Main] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and it gets -20000 power for the turn. Then, play up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 4 or less and 《Universe》 in its special traits from your hand.

detail.name: 空前絶後の超決戦!
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン】相手のバトルカード1枚までを選び、このターン中、パワー-20000。その後、自分の手札のコスト4以下の《宇宙》を含む特徴を持つバトルカード1枚までを登場させる。
